    "Id": "697658",
    "ThreadId": "279314",
    "Html": "\r\n<p>If changed Template to TabControl is empty, example:</p>\r\n<p>&lt;ControlTemplate x:Key=&quot;mykey&quot; TargetType=&quot;{x:Type l:BivTabControl}&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Grid&gt;&lt;/Grid&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;/ControlTemplate&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>and apply this ControlTemplate to style:</p>\r\n<p>&lt;Setter Property=&quot;Template&quot; Value=&quot;{StaticResource mykey}&quot;/&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Result, Content TabControl&nbsp; is empty, but I set View to TabControl Region.</p>\r\n<p>If I Changed ither Template, example:</p>\r\n<p>&lt;ControlTemplate x:Key=&quot;mykey&quot; TargetType=&quot;{x:Type l:BivTabControl}&quot;&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;Grid&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;ScrollViewer Visibility=&quot;Hidden&quot; &gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;TabPanel x:Name=&quot;TabPanel&quot; IsItemsHost=&quot;True&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/ScrollViewer&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/Grid&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&lt;/ControlTemplate&gt;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>this work - Content is <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span>contains my View.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"en\"><span>How do I</span> <span>make sure</span>\r\n<span>not to</span> <span>put</span> <span>fake</span> elements<span>?:</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&lt;ScrollViewer Visibility=&quot;Hidden&quot; &gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;TabPanel x:Name=&quot;TabPanel&quot; IsItemsHost=&quot;True&quot; /&gt;<br>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &lt;/ScrollViewer&gt;</p>\r\n",
